* Two Pipeline\nApproaches
** Notebooks
***_ Procedural (step-by-step)
***_ Full control over execution
***_ Explicit read/transform/write
** Lakeflow Declarative
***_ Declare desired end state
***_ System manages orchestration
***_ Automatic parallelization
***_ Automatic error recovery
** Key Difference
***_ Notebooks: HOW to process
***_ Declarative: WHAT result to produce
@endmindmap
